ROME, Ga. -- As the high school football season inches closer to the playoffs, the stakes are high in the #Team11 Game of the Week brought to you by Academy Sports + Outdoors when Model takes on Chattooga. Getting ready for the big game! 
The Chattooga Indians and Model Blue Devils each only have one blemish to their records. It's a big one! Who will win? Watch full coverage tonight at 10:30 p.m. on The ATL and at 11 on 11Alive!
